        <li>Pick from a range of 'visualizations' to suit your reading style (bigger links are more important, hotter colors are items on the rise)</li>
        <li>If multiple sources mention the same url (e.g. <a href="http://trendsmap.com">http://trendsmap.com</a>) then those items are combined and considered more important</li>
